 \begin{pmatrix} y_0 \\ y_1 \\ y_2 \\ \vdots \\ y_{n-1} \\ y_n \end{pmatrix} \mapsto \frac1{y_0+1} \begin{pmatrix} y_1 \\ y_2 \\ \vdots \\ y_{n-1} \\ y_n \end{pmatrix} =: \begin{pmatrix} x_1 \\ x_2 \\ \vdots \\ x_{n-1} \\ x_n \end{pmatrix} \mapsto \frac{2}{1-2x_n+\lVert x\rVert^2} \begin{pmatrix}x_1\\x_2\\\vdots\\x_{n-1}\\1-x_n\end{pmatrix} - \begin{pmatrix}0\\0\\\vdots\\0\\1\end{pmatrix} =: \begin{pmatrix}z_1\\z_2\\\vdots\\z_{n-1}\\z_n\end{pmatrix} 
 \begin{pmatrix} y_0 \\ y_1 \\ y_2 \\ \vdots \\ y_{n-1} \\ y_n \end{pmatrix} \mapsto \frac{2}{1+y_0-2y_n+\frac{\sum_{i=1}^n y_i^2}{1+y_0}} \begin{pmatrix}y_1\\y_2\\\vdots\\y_{n-1}\\1+y_0-y_n\end{pmatrix} - \begin{pmatrix}0\\0\\\vdots\\0\\1\end{pmatrix} =: \begin{pmatrix}z_1\\z_2\\\vdots\\z_{n-1}\\z_n\end{pmatrix} 
